edu.umd.cs.guitar.replayer
Class Replayer

java.lang.Object
  edu.umd.cs.guitar.replayer.Replayer

public class Replayer
extends java.lang.Object

Main replayer class, monitoring the replayer's behaviors Note on exception handling: GUITAR related exceptions MUST be derived from GExceptions. All non GException exceptions are to be considered as AUT exceptions (unless explicitly stated and handled, in an itemised manner). All "caught" exceptions MUST be propagated upwards unless expplicitly itemised.

Author:
Bao Nguyen
